  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"RootIndex 3 StartRoot p squared EndRoot equals t Superscript nine sevenths\"><mroot><msup><mi>p</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>3</mn></mroot><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>t</mi><mfrac><mn>9</mn><mn>7</mn></mfrac></msup></math></p>\n<p>In the given equation, <math alttext=\"p greater than 1\"><mi>p</mi><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>1</mn></math> and <math alttext=\"t greater than 1\"><mi>t</mi><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>. If <math alttext=\"t equals p Superscript 3 n minus 1\"><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>p</mi><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>n</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>, where <math alttext=\"n\"><mi>n</mi>\n</math> is a constant, what is the value of <math alttext=\"n\"><mi>n</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
